OL,3,CPeople can report crime through mobile
OL,4,Capp under Jersey Police trial
OL,6,FA free mobile app which allows victims
OL,7,Fand witnesses to report crimes and
OL,8,Fsubmit evidence to police is now
OL,9,Favailable in Jersey.
OL,11,FThe Kulpa app, developed by local
OL,12,Fcompany Kulpa Platforms Ltd, is being
OL,13,Ftrialled for 12 months with support
OL,14,Ffrom Digital Jersey.
