OL,3,CPeople can report crime through mobile
OL,4,Capp under Jersey Police trial
OL,6,FIt is already used in the UK and has
OL,7,Fbeen proven to save officers an
OL,8,Faverage of seven hours per case, as
OL,9,Fmembers of the public can upload
OL,10,Fdigital evidence such as photos,
OL,11,Fvideos and screenshots of social media
OL,12,Fmessages.
OL,14,F"They don't have to share that with us
OL,15,Fstraight away," Detective Chief
OL,16,FInspector Mark Hafey from the States
OL,17,Fof Jersey Police explains.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/6
