OL,6,F"They can hold on to that evidence as
OL,7,Flong as they want and then when they
OL,8,Ffeel ready to share it, they have the
OL,9,Fability to do so."
OL,11,FJersey Police says submitting evidence
OL,12,Fthrough the secure app reduces the
OL,13,Fneed for them to seize a device to
OL,14,Fdownload that material.
OL,16,F"Devices nowadays can hold up to one
OL,17,Fterabyte of data," DCI Hafey adds.
OL,18,F"That's the equivalent of 1,300 filing
OL,19,Fcabinets of printed text.
