OL,6,F"This is a huge step forward in terms
OL,7,Fof ensuring the victim or witness
OL,8,Fprivacy, improving the timelines of
OL,9,Finvestigations, and bringing offenders
OL,10,Fto justice as quickly as possible."
OL,12,FHowever, Tracey Le Brocq, Chief
OL,13,FExecutive Officer at Jersey Action
OL,14,FAgainst Rape, says that it could
OL,15,Fincrease the danger for some victims
OL,16,Fif the app is discovered on their
OL,17,Fphone.
