OL,6,F"The abuser identifying that app and
OL,7,Fseeing what is being documented could
OL,8,Fmean a high risk for individuals," she
OL,9,Fexplains.
OL,11,F"It's not necessarily the app on its
OL,12,Fown, it's ensuring you continue that
OL,13,Fhuman interaction as well."
OL,15,FThe force stresses that crimes can
OL,16,Fstill be reported conventionally, with
OL,17,Fthe app designed to offer an extra
OL,18,Foption for those who need it, rather
OL,19,Fthan replacing in-person visits.
